  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Acute acoustic trauma is a growing concern in the IDF. there is currently no accepted
      treatment. The present retrospective study is intended to evaluate the efficacy of different
      treatment modalities in the IDF between 01/01/2010 and 15/06/2020.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
